    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine and transmission are strong, and it drives smoothly with no mechanical issues. While the exterior and interior are clean and presentable, you may find some minor signs of normal wear such as small stone chips on the hood and slight creasing on the driver's seat leather. It is a reliable, solid car that is ready for its next owner.",
