    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in impeccable condition. This specimen exhibits no cosmetic or mechanical compromises, having been preserved to the highest standards. The exterior retains its original factory luster, while the interior remains indistinguishable from its initial delivery state. This is a definitive opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle of peerless integrity and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
